---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="baptism by ice" description="walk long enough and things separate on their own">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-faint mb-4">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">writing</a> <span class="text-faint">/</span> baptism-by-ice
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-normal animate-fade-up">baptism by ice</h1>

    <div class="space-y-10 mt-10 animate-fade-up delay-1">
      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">1/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">out here it's different</p>
        <p>things get decided faster</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">2/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">no dashboards</p>
        <p>no noise</p>
        <p>just terrain and weather</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-dim">not much room to argue with either</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">3/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">plans look clean before starting</p>
        <p>less clean once elevation shows up</p>
        <p class="mt-3">time stretches</p>
        <p class="text-dim">distance doesn't care</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">4/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">first instinct is to push through</p>
        <p>keep the same pace as before</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-dim">that burns out quickly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">5/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">after a while the rhythm settles</p>
        <p>step</p>
        <p>breath</p>
        <p>step</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-dim">attention narrows</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">6/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">turns out most things don't need to be solved</p>
        <p class="text-dim">just seen clearly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">7/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">a lot of assumptions don't make it back</p>
        <p>they feel obvious out here</p>
        <p class="text-dim">harder to justify later</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">8/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">same pattern everywhere</p>
        <p>contact removes a lot of clever ideas</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-dim">simpler paths tend to hold</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">9/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">nothing dramatic about it</p>
        <p class="text-dim">just less room to lie to yourself</p>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-post">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint">10/</span>
        <p class="mt-2">walk long enough</p>
        <p>and things separate on their own</p>
        <p class="mt-3">what matters</p>
        <p class="text-dim">what doesn't</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <img src="/images/baptism-by-ice.jpg" alt="Laguna de los Tres, Patagonia — frozen lake beneath snow-covered mountains" class="w-full rounded-xl" />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">← back to writing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .thread-post {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(212, 168, 100, 0.12);
  }

  .thread-post p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
